      "title": "A 02-day debate on child and maternal malnutrition",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A two-day debate is scheduled to be held in Parliament tomorrow (6th) and the day after (7th) regarding the report issued by UNICEF regarding the malnutrition situation of children and mothers in this country.",
        "The proposal for the debate is presented by the Samagi Jana Balawegaya Party."
